title: How to check manufacture date of new Pixel 3 phone without unboxing it? I have the IMEI & SKU no's
content: How to check manufacture date of new Pixel 3 (G013A model) phone without unboxing it? I have the IMEI, SKU and barcode numbers. I tried the website imeipro.info but it doesn't give me the manufacture date or even where it's made
